# Frontend Component Rules

## Component Architecture

```
frontend/src/components/
├── ui/           ← Base design system (Button, Input, Card, Modal, Badge, Toast)
├── layout/       ← Navbar, Sidebar, Footer, Shell
├── auth/         ← LoginForm, OtpInput
├── menu/         ← MenuGrid, ItemCard, CategoryChip, CartDrawer
├── order/        ← OrderCard, OrderStatus, KDSCard
├── billing/      ← BillPreview, ReceiptTemplate, PaymentButton ✅ EXISTS
├── admin/        ← DashboardStats, RevenueChart, QuickActions
├── storefront/   ← HeroCarousel, GoogleReviews, InstagramFeed
└── common/       ← SearchBar, ImageUpload, PriceDisplay
```

## Must Follow

- **React Server Components** by default. Use `"use client"` only when needed
- **Tailwind CSS 4** for all styling. NO inline `style={{}}` props
- **Lucide React** for icons. No other icon libraries
- **`@/` imports** only. No `../../` relative paths
- **Mobile-first** design. Test at 375px minimum
- **Semantic HTML** with proper heading hierarchy
- **ARIA labels** on all icon-only buttons
- **Dark mode** via `class="dark"` strategy

## Price Display

Always format prices from paise:
```typescript
// Price is stored in paise in DB
const displayPrice = `₹${(priceInPaise / 100).toFixed(2)}`

// For calculations, stay in paise (integers)
const subtotalPaise = items.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.price * item.qty, 0)
const cgstPaise = Math.round(subtotalPaise * 0.025) // 2.5%
const sgstPaise = Math.round(subtotalPaise * 0.025) // 2.5%
const totalPaise = subtotalPaise + cgstPaise + sgstPaise
```

